<b>Exercise</b>
</p>
<p>
In this question, you must implement the <tt>shred()</tt>
function, which takes two parameters:
<ul>
<li> <tt>infd</tt> ... a file descriptor open for reading
<li> <tt>outfd</tt> ... a file descriptor open for writing
</ul>
and does the following:
</p>
<pre>
for each 128-byte block in <i>infd</i> {
   read the block into a buffer
   overwrite the buffer with random characters
   write the buffer to <i>outfd</i>
}
</pre>
